Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:12.44,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トロンコ そろそろ巡回は来るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.44,Default,van,0,0,0,,Tronco, it's about time for the cops to make their rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:15.04,花語製作通用-ja,,0,0,0,,本字幕由✿花語&千夏字幕組✿共同製作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:15.40,Default,tor,0,0,0,,Why don't we just grease their palms a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:15.40,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サツなんて ちょっと労いしときゃいいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:18.18,Default,van,0,0,0,,Scusa's not satisfied with "a little."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:18.18,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スクーサ様はちょっとじゃ済まなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.49,Default,tor,0,0,0,,Scusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.49,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スクーサ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.82,Default,van,0,0,0,,The new Federal Bureau of Prohibition head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.93,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,新任の連邦取締官だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:25.18,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコ ファミリーの至高タマ貰ってるらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:24.98,Default,van,0,0,0,,I hear he's taken a small fortune from the Orco family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:34.45,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 大した運転だな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.45,Default,van,0,0,0,,Hey, watch your driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:37.25,Default,van,0,0,0,,I thought you'd been driving taxis up 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:37.25,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この間までタクシー 転がしてたんだろうがよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:40.20,Default,tor,0,0,0,,All the booze in the back is throwing us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:40.40,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,血に積みまくった酒で振られるんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.86,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お陰で稼ぎが違うんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:43.86,Default,van,0,0,0,,But it's putting more money in your pockets, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:47.14,Default,tor,0,0,0,,Mr. Vanno, once I save up enough, I'm gonna buy a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:47.14,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴァンノさん 俺稼いだら車買うんです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.31,Default,tor,0,0,0,,A Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.51,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファントム
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:49.29,Default,van,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:52.65,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後百回酒運んだら 俺が買ってやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:52.65,Default,van,0,0,0,,A hundred more booze runs, and I'll buy one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.20,Default,tor,0,0,0,,Really?! I'll hold you to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.38,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当ですか 約束ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:58.61,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ二人共生きてたらな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.41,Default,van,0,0,0,,Assuming we're both still alive, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:03.85,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,来たぞ 急げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.65,Default,van,0,0,0,,It's them. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.15,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,隠れろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:25.95,Default,van,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:55.50,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,行ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.30,Default,van,0,0,0,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:57.80,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい トロンコ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.80,Default,van,0,0,0,,Hey, Tronco.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.30,Default,van,0,0,0,,We're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.50,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.32,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:01.14,Default,van,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.67,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさと戻ろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:09.48,Default,van,0,0,0,,Let's get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.76,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後一匹残ってるな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.57,Default,ser,0,0,0,,There's one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:58.97,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,始末しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.77,Default,ser,0,0,0,,Put him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:29.06,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
