Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.60,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコとはもう戦争するしなねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.40,Default,van,0,0,0,,I tell you, it's war against the Orcos now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.26,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.26,Default,van,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.93,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You clung to the underside of the truck to escape, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.93,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トラックにしがみついて逃げ出すなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.68,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Pretty smart thinking, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.88,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前にしちゃ 上出来だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.56,Default,av,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.31,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おぉ 遅かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.11,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.23,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,親父が喜ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.03,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Dad's gonna love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.94,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや お祝いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.94,Default,av,0,0,0,,No, it's a gift for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.03,Default,av,0,0,0,,Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.23,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,飲んでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.37,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれと比べると 大分見劣りするけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:50.25,Default,av,0,0,0,,Though I realize it hardly compares to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.95,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファントム
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.95,Default,nero,0,0,0,,A Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.52,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's from the Galassias.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.52,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガラシアからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.54,Default,av,0,0,0,,Galassias?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.73,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガラシア?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.26,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱいけてんな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:59.06,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That's good stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:05.52,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,花婿はシカゴを牛耳るドン ガラシアの甥だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.54,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The groom is the nephew of Don Galassia,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:05.34,Default,nero,0,0,0,,the guy who controls Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:09.13,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この町はヴァッティが仕切ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.91,Default,van,0,0,0,,The Vanettis own this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.66,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガラシアの手助けなんていらねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.66,Default,van,0,0,0,,We don't need the Galassias' help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:15.98,Default,av,0,0,0,,Funny, I heard you lost some turf downtown to the Orco family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:16.09,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ダウンタウンの島は\Nオルコファミリに取られたって聞いたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.00,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言葉には気を付けろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.81,Default,van,0,0,0,,You'd better watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.17,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:19.97,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.76,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,親父さんが呼んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.77,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Your father is calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.25,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.80,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.65,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,バルベロ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.65,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Barbero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.34,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のここだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.20,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The brains of my operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:31.06,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アヴィリオにコルテオ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.73,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Avilio and Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:34.29,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よろしく 話は聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.86,Default,bar,0,0,0,,A pleasure. I've heard all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.90,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ 楽しんでいってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.70,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Well, have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.12,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうこ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.12,Default,cor,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:44.79,Default,cor,0,0,0,,We came here because we needed the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:44.99,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お金が必要だからってここに来たのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.91,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなところ 早く出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:52.93,Default,cor,0,0,0,,We need to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:56.05,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく来たんだ 楽しめよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.85,Default,av,0,0,0,,It's a party. Let's enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:02.14,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,劇場の方はどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.85,Default,vin,0,0,0,,How's the playhouse coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:03.73,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,順調だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.73,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's all going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.96,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Should be done by the end of June.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.96,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,六月いっぱいには完成する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:10.45,Default,fla,0,0,0,,Big Brother, Don Galassia's decided to come to the big opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:10.63,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄さん 杮落としには\Nドン ガラシアも来ることになったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.59,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後三ヶ月だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.57,Default,fla,0,0,0,,We've got three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.90,Default,fla,0,0,0,,Then Vanetti, Orco, and Galassia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:17.13,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで ヴァッティ オルコ ガラシア
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:20.40,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,三つのファミリーが一度に会することになる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.21,Default,fla,0,0,0,,All three families will be in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.72,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それでどうなる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.38,Default,nero,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:25.70,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに最近のオルコに目に余る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.70,Default,fla,0,0,0,,I know the Orcos have been overstepping lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:29.84,Default,fla,0,0,0,,but they have to do as the Galassias say, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:29.84,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 奴らはガラシアの言葉には\N従わなきゃならない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.63,Default,nero,0,0,0,,So do we.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.84,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達ヴァッティもだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.56,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はもう長くない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.56,Default,vin,0,0,0,,I don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:44.30,Default,vin,0,0,0,,But I intend to leave the family on solid footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:44.45,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だがなぁ ファミリーの土台だけは\Nしっかりさせておくつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.99,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから姉さんはガラシアの甥と結婚した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.92,Default,fla,0,0,0,,That's why Sis is marrying Galassia's nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:51.02,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ロナルドはいいやつだし 信用出来る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:51.03,Default,fla,0,0,0,,Ronaldo's a good guy. We can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.22,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほぼなにも問題...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.22,Default,fla,0,0,0,,Nothing left to worry—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.61,Default,nero,0,0,0,,They killed another of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.80,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,また一人やられた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.36,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコの酒を取ったからだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:57.37,Default,fla,0,0,0,,That's because we stole Orco's booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:00.74,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのルートも三ヶ月前まではうちのもんだった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:08:00.60,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That route was ours until three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:04.92,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえの島も守れねぇファミリーに先はねぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:04.72,Default,nero,0,0,0,,A family that can't protect their own turf has no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.99,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一本どうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.80,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Care for a cigar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:15.93,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,葉巻ってやつだが 煙を吸うんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.80,Default,vin,0,0,0,,With a cigar, you don't inhale smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.96,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,時間を吸うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.76,Default,vin,0,0,0,,You inhale time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:20.86,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よく考えろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.73,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Think carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.42,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてゆっくりと歩め
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.23,Default,vin,0,0,0,,then walk forward with purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:28.31,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,速く走ろうとするものほど転びやすいものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:28.11,Default,vin,0,0,0,,The faster you rush out, the more likely you are to trip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:37.89,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自ら動かぬものに天は\Nその手を差し伸べずとも言うぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:37.69,Default,nero,0,0,0,,There's another saying: "God helps those who help themselves."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.59,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.39,Default,van,0,0,0,,That piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:59.33,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,フィオを泣かせやがったら 俺がぶっ殺してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:59.29,Default,van,0,0,0,,If he makes Fio cry, I'll beat the crap out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.56,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ご機嫌斜めだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.35,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I see you're in a foul mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.92,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ロナルド様の御なりった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.72,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I think Master Ronaldo is paying us a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.29,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おめでどう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.09,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:27.79,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,晴れて私も君たちのファミリーというわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.59,Default,ron,0,0,0,,I'm now officially a member of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.46,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ネロは?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.46,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Where's Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.96,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Don Vanetti requested his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:33.16,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドン ヴァネッティとちょっとな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:38.60,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,娘の結婚式にも顔を出さないで 閉じこもってる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:38.31,Default,ron,0,0,0,,He's locked up in his room, and won't even come to his own daughter's wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:42.09,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,用心深さもすぎれば臆病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.89,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Too much caution just becomes cowardice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.18,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,表には伏せているんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.18,Default,bar,0,0,0,,We're keeping this within the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:50.06,Default,bar,0,0,0,,but he's staying indoors on his doctor's recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:50.10,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,外に出るのは医者から控えるようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:54.67,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ オルコとのことは私がどうにかする
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:54.23,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Well, I'll fix your little Orco problem for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:59.80,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大体こんなしけた町で\Nちまちま争っている意味が分からないね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:59.74,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Not that I get the point of fighting over this backwater burg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:04.19,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たかが国境からきた酒を運ぶ通り道だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:03.99,Default,ron,0,0,0,,It's just a pit stop on the way of hauling booze over the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.82,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.62,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.10,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,滑稽だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.90,Default,av,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.60,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何がだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.42,Default,ron,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:17.53,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トラの威を借るキツネは滑稽だと言っている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:17.34,Default,av,0,0,0,,Watching an ass strut around in a lion's skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.06,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえいったい誰の...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.86,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Who the hell do you think—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.94,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.94,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Stop it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.02,Default,fio,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.21,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.47,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつまでも子供ね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.27,Default,fio,0,0,0,,You'll never grow up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.41,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お似合いだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.21,Default,van,0,0,0,,They're a perfect couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.82,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,下戸は辛いな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.64,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Teetotalers have it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.24,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.05,Default,av,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.93,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これが例の酒か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.73,Default,bar,0,0,0,,This is the liquor you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.58,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,凄いキックだな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.58,Default,bar,0,0,0,,It's got quite a kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.82,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Where do you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.01,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこで作ってる?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:23.18,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,キッチン アパートの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.99,Default,cor,0,0,0,,The kitchen... in my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.20,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.20,Default,van,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.04,Default,van,0,0,0,,I haven't seen that look on your face in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.04,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のそんな顔久しぶりだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.41,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Can we talk in private?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.60,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと話せるか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.55,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,虎の威を借る狐か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.35,Default,van,0,0,0,,An ass in a lion's skin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:44.09,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,口も達者なんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.89,Default,van,0,0,0,,You have a way with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.76,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,改めてになるが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:47.55,Default,van,0,0,0,,I don't think we've been introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.80,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴァンノ クレメンテだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.60,Default,van,0,0,0,,Vanno Clemente.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.71,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ ブルノ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.51,Default,av,0,0,0,,Avilio Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.59,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたとは上手くやっていけそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.39,Default,av,0,0,0,,I think we'll make a good team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:00.07,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:03.02,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,味わって食え
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:03.03,Default,van,0,0,0,,Enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:07.14,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴァンノ様特製 ローレス風チョッピーノだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:06.95,Default,van,0,0,0,,This is Maestro Vanno's special Lawless-style cioppino.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.34,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,旨そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.24,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:10.31,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.12,Default,van,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:23.05,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,父よ あなたの慈しみに\N感謝してこの食事を頂きます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:22.84,Default,van,0,0,0,,Father in Heaven, we thank you for the meal in which we now partake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:27.29,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私達の心と体を支える糧としてください
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:27.09,Default,van,0,0,0,,We pray that it might nourish our bodies and our souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.97,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.63,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.88,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ痛むのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.68,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.71,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらくは飯抜きで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.51,Default,tig,0,0,0,,I won't be eating for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:47.93,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういや あのアヴィリオってやつ おもしれいな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:47.87,Default,van,0,0,0,,That reminds me. That Avilio guy's pretty interesting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:51.99,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒にいたコルテオってやつの酒も 相当いける
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:52.00,Default,bar,0,0,0,,And that Corteo fellow who was with him makes a mean brew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:55.74,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコと無駄にやり合わなくて済むな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.75,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah. Maybe we won't have to press things with the Orcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.66,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それについじゃ ドンと話したんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.46,Default,van,0,0,0,,You talked to the don about that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:03.20,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい ネロ ファンゴはやるんだろうな?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:03.01,Default,van,0,0,0,,Hey, Nero. We're taking out Fango, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.12,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:06.93,Default,nero,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.30,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.30,Default,van,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:14.12,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Galassia wants the Vanettis and the Orcos to make nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:14.32,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガラシアは俺達ヴァッティと\Nオルコの手打ちをご所望だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.27,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.27,Default,van,0,0,0,,That's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.50,Default,van,0,0,0,,How's Tronco supposed to rest in peace, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.50,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ トロンコは浮かばれね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.90,Default,van,0,0,0,,I'll do it myself if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.07,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺一人でもやる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.22,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,酔ってんのか ヴァンノ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.22,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Are you drunk, Vanno?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.70,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコには勝てても ガラシアとは...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.78,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Even if you could beat the Orcos, the Galassias...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.08,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やってもみねで 勝つも負けるもあるがよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:29.08,Default,van,0,0,0,,We won't know if we don't even try!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.61,Default,bar,0,0,0,,We need funds first. If we had that booze—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.61,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは資金だ あの酒さえあ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:32.83,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.02,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし やるか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:37.51,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.21,Default,nero,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:41.10,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,引き金を引くのは俺達じゃねがな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:40.90,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We won't be the ones pulling the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.63,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:44.25,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.25,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本気なの?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.25,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.97,Default,av,0,0,0,,If I take out Fango, I can join the family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:49.16,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファンゴをやれば ファミリに入れるんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.67,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,話持って来といたなんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.43,Default,van,0,0,0,,I know I'm the one who brought it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:55.97,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつは危ねぇ仕事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.97,Default,van,0,0,0,,but this is a dangerous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.24,Default,van,0,0,0,,They recently killed one of our young guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.24,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この間も若いのが殺された
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:13:59.52,Default,av,0,0,0,,Let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:13:59.72,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やらせてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.32,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,水曜の夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.32,Default,van,0,0,0,,Wednesday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.93,Default,van,0,0,0,,He'll be spending some time at Lacrima's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.93,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,奴は必ずラクリマの家で過ごす
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:08.99,Default,av,0,0,0,,Lacrima?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.01,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ラクリマ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.87,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファンゴの愛人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.80,Default,van,0,0,0,,Fango's mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:14.08,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ローレスクロニクルの\N向かえのアパートに住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:13.88,Default,van,0,0,0,,Her apartment's across from the Lawless Chronicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.46,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういつはどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.26,Default,av,0,0,0,,What should I do about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:20.32,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒にやっちまえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.13,Default,van,0,0,0,,Eh, you can kill her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.59,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これまでに殺しは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:23.39,Default,van,0,0,0,,Ever killed before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:25.54,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:25.54,Default,av,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:26.71,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.71,Default,van,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:29.68,Default,van,0,0,0,,Well, you're getting a late start, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:29.70,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ お前の年じゃ遅いくらいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.75,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おれん時は...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.55,Default,van,0,0,0,,My first was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.56,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,また連絡する
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.36,Default,van,0,0,0,,I'll be in touch later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.87,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな奴らと一緒になって正気じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.67,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You're joining up with guys like him? That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:50.57,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.73,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なにもかも狂ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.53,Default,av,0,0,0,,The whole world's gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:06.54,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,親父の親友ってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.30,Default,av,0,0,0,,They claim to be my dad's best friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.25,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,復讐に協力したいそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.05,Default,av,0,0,0,,and want to help me with my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.70,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,奇妙な話だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.30,Default,av,0,0,0,,Bizarre, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:21.76,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ご丁寧に 大切な物を奪った奴らの名前まで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.06,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'm handed everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.53,Default,av,0,0,0,,even the names of the men who stole the people I loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:34.13,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,残り半分は上手く行ってからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:34.13,Default,van,0,0,0,,You'll get the other half after you succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.58,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ うん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:40.81,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫 何も問題はない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:40.61,Default,av,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.22,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.02,Default,ser,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:10.61,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,くっせ ったく どんだけ飲んでんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:10.46,Default,ser,0,0,0,,You stink. Just how soused are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.42,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい ここで寝んな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:13.09,Default,ser,0,0,0,,Hey! You can't sleep here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:16.09,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,友達が住んでるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.70,Default,av,0,0,0,,My friend lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.81,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,知るかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.62,Default,ser,0,0,0,,You think I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.53,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら ささっと失せろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.38,Default,ser,0,0,0,,Go on, get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.20,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,セルペンテさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.00,Default,che,0,0,0,,Mr. Serpente!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:25.77,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,丁度いいや
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.77,Default,che,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.71,Default,ser,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.74,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なにか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.92,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,家ね 上等なのが入ったんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.38,Default,che,0,0,0,,I got some good stuff in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.49,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここじゃ目に付くんで 車の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.29,Default,che,0,0,0,,We're too conspicuous here. Let's go to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:11.58,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ そうだ 力を込めろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:11.38,Default,fan,0,0,0,,That's right. Harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:16.90,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと もっとだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.70,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Harder! Harder, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:34.60,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,休んでないで さっさと来いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:34.40,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Don't stop. Keep it coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:37.34,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とんだ豚ね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.17,Default,lac,0,0,0,,You filthy pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:40.90,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,豚 豚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.70,Default,lac,0,0,0,,Pig! Pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:59.19,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドア開ける前にはノックしろってママに\N教わらなかったのか ボイー
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:59.19,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Didn't your mama ever teach you to knock, little boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.64,Default,lac,0,0,0,,Please... Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.84,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと やめてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.14,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.14,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:10.79,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I'm getting chills all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:11.25,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たまんなぇ ぞくぞくする
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:15.81,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しくなってきた てめぇも一緒にやるか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:15.81,Default,fan,0,0,0,,This is getting fun! You wanna join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.86,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Go on! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.86,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら 来い 打ってみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:21.45,Default,lac,0,0,0,,Don't fire... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:21.64,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やめて 撃たないで お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:28.21,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,早く撃ち込んで来いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:28.21,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Come on, shoot one off already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.63,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Fire that bad boy real good...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.82,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大事なあれでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.88,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.68,Default,ser,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:08.02,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファンゴは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:07.82,Default,van,0,0,0,,Where's Fango?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:11.26,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逃がしちまったか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.06,Default,van,0,0,0,,He got away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:12.63,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.23,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.05,Default,av,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.55,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相手が相手だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.55,Default,van,0,0,0,,We knew he was a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.80,Default,van,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.00,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかたねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.21,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,此奴か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.01,Default,van,0,0,0,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:31.50,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴァネッティのあんたがオルコの人間を\Nやるのはまずいんじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:31.39,Default,av,0,0,0,,Won't it make trouble if a Vanetti like you kills an Orco?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.16,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オールドビレッジの墓行く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.96,Default,van,0,0,0,,We'll go to the graveyard in the old village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:39.16,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サツだ 先に行っててくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.96,Default,av,0,0,0,,It's the cops. I'll meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:59.55,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,われ 主の限りなく嫌い給う罪を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:59.34,Default,van,0,0,0,,O my God, I am heartily sorry for having offended thee,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:59.34,720通用注釋-ja,,0,0,0,,這是天主教的「痛悔經」,直接copy經文的文言翻譯了,\N為了順應字幕長度,不會與日譯語序對照...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:04.17,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,限りなく愛すべき御父に背きしを深く悔み奉る
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:03.97,Default,van,0,0,0,,and I detest all my sins because of thy just punishments,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:09.82,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,御子イエズス キリストの\N流し給える御血の功徳によりて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:09.68,Default,van,0,0,0,,but most of all because they offend thee, my God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:12.36,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わが罪を赦し給え
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.27,Default,van,0,0,0,,who art all good and deserving of all my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:16.53,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,聖寵の助けをもって今より心を改め
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:16.40,Default,van,0,0,0,,I firmly resolve, with the help of thy grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:23.48,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,再び罪を犯して 御心に\N背くことあるまじと決心し奉る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:23.28,Default,van,0,0,0,,to sin no more and avoid the near occasions of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.52,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アーメン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.32,Default,van,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:31.28,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この下にトロンコが眠ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:31.08,Default,van,0,0,0,,This is where we laid Tronco to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.83,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気のいいやつだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.83,Default,van,0,0,0,,He was a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.37,Default,van,0,0,0,,He liked cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.57,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車がすきだった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:38.69,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.50,Default,van,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.93,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,セルペンテ 祈れ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.73,Default,van,0,0,0,,Serpente. Start praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:48.77,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:48.60,Default,ser,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:51.88,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,死にたくねぇよ お願いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:51.68,Default,ser,0,0,0,,I don't want to die! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:54.44,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何も誰もやらねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.44,Default,ser,0,0,0,,I won't kill anyone ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.73,Default,ser,0,0,0,,I'll cut ties with Orco and Fango.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.05,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコ ファンゴとも縁を切る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.86,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トロンコの前で殺すのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.86,Default,ser,0,0,0,,You're going to kill me in front of Tronco?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.61,Default,ser,0,0,0,,You'll stain his grave with blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.61,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,墓を血で汚すのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.92,Default,van,0,0,0,,Not gonna pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.92,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,祈らないのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.53,Default,ser,0,0,0,,Don't do this! I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.73,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌だよ 死にたくねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.46,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:07.37,Default,van,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:09.35,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.16,Default,ser,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.99,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく 罰当たりの野郎だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:18.79,Default,van,0,0,0,,May God have mercy on your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.92,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.68,Default,av,0,0,0,,That night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.56,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の家族をやったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.43,Default,av,0,0,0,,The ones who killed my family were
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.64,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴィンセントヴァネッティ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.39,Default,av,0,0,0,,Vincente Vanetti,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:32.13,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,息子のNero
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:31.93,Default,av,0,0,0,,his son Nero...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:34.00,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.80,Default,av,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:36.07,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴァンノ クレメンテ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.87,Default,av,0,0,0,,Vanno Clemente.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.66,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.54,Default,van,0,0,0,,Who are... you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.93,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の名はアンジェロ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:58.93,Default,av,0,0,0,,My name is Angelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:00.50,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'm the son of a man you killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:00.65,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らに殺された
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:03.35,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,テスタ ラグーザの息子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:03.15,Default,av,0,0,0,,The son of Testa Lagusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:06.51,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:36.01,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:39.24,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:39.24,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:41.50,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,此奴の言い分を聞いてからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:41.31,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Let's hear his side of it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.65,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴァンノが銃を奪われて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:44.57,Default,av,0,0,0,,He stole Vanno's gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:48.29,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がセルペンテを撃ったが 遅かった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:48.09,Default,av,0,0,0,,I shot Serpente, but it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:50.71,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,縄を掛けなかったのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:50.71,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Your hands weren't tied?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:53.20,Default,av,0,0,0,,Serpente said he'd let me pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:53.50,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,祈らせてくれっとセルペンテが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:55.82,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それでヴァンノが縄を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:55.74,Default,av,0,0,0,,Then he tied up Vanno...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.82,0:23:57.33,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,連れて行け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:23:57.24,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Take me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:23:58.82,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その場所に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:23:58.62,Default,nero,0,0,0,,To where it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.51,0:24:04.20,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:04.17,Default,av,0,0,0,,Over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:06.37,單語720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二人が...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.17,Default,av,0,0,0,,That's where they...
